s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:460:\"<p>What is cornerstone content, and how can it help improve your search rankings? You&#8217;ve likely heard the term &#8220;cornerstone content&#8221; being thrown around as you look for SEO and content marketing tips. But what exactly is cornerstone content, and why&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-cornerstone-content/\">What is Cornerstone Content? Plus Tips and Examples</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29697:\"<p>What is cornerstone content, and how can it help improve your search rankings?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ve likely heard the term &#8220;cornerstone content&#8221; being thrown around as you look for SEO and content marketing tips. But what exactly is cornerstone content, and why is it essential for your SEO strategy?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we will explain cornerstone content, why itâ€™s important, and even show you how to create it!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-cornerstone-content-plus-examples\">What is Cornerstone Content (Plus Examples)?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-characteristics-of-cornerstone-content\">Characteristics of Cornerstone Content</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-importance-of-cornerstone-content-for-seo\">The Importance of Cornerstone Content for SEO</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-improved-search-rankings\">Improved Search Rankings</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-enhanced-user-experience\">Enhanced User Experience</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-authority-building\">Authority Building</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-internal-linking-the-key-to-optimizing-cornerstone-content-in-wordpress\">Internal Linking: The Key to Optimizing Cornerstone Content in WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-manual-internal-linking\">Manual Internal Linking</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-using-the-cornerstone-content-feature-in-aioseo\">Using the Cornerstone Content Feature in AIOSEO</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-cornerstone-content-5-best-practices-for-better-rankings\">Cornerstone Content: 5 Best Practices for Better Rankings</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-conduct-keyword-research\">1. Conduct Keyword Research</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-create-scannable-content\">2. Create Scannable Content</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-use-a-table-of-contents\">3. Use a Table of Contents</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-add-an-faq-section\">4. Add an FAQ Section</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-keep-your-cornerstone-content-fresh\">5. Keep Your Cornerstone Content Fresh</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-cornerstone-content-your-faqs-answered\">What is Cornerstone Content: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-cornerstone-content\">What is cornerstone content?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-is-cornerstone-content-important-for-my-website\">Why is cornerstone content important for my website?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-the-best-tool-for-creating-cornerstone-content\">What is the best tool for creating cornerstone content?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-implement-your-cornerstone-content-strategy-today\">Implement Your Cornerstone Content Strategy Today</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-cornerstone-content-plus-examples\">What is Cornerstone Content (Plus Examples)?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornerstone content, sometimes called pillar content, refers to the foundational set of web pages or articles on your website. These are typically comprehensive, in-depth, and highly informative, covering core topics central to your site&#8217;s overall subject or theme.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating cornerstone content is a powerful content marketing strategy with phenomenal results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornerstone content serves several important purposes in SEO and content marketing. Typical examples include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Authority and expertise</strong>: Cornerstone content helps you establish topical authority. It also helps you better showcase your expertise. Both are important elements in meeting <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-google-eat/\" title=\"What is Google E-E-A-T?  Understanding Googleâ€™s Secret Sauce for Creating Effective Content\">Googleâ€™s E-E-A-T quality standards</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Improved crawling</strong>: Creating cornerstone content helps you create a more optimized internal linking structure. This improves crawling by search bots and boosts your SEO.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Improved indexing</strong>: When search engines identify your cornerstone content, they can better index it for relevant search terms.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to up your SEO game, then cornerstone content must be part of your content strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-characteristics-of-cornerstone-content\">Characteristics of Cornerstone Content</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you create your cornerstone content strategy, itâ€™s important to know what type of content constitutes cornerstone content. Here are a few characteristics of cornerstone content:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Relevant</strong>: Covers a topic that is central to your niche or industry.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Comprehensive</strong>: Provides in-depth information, often serving as the ultimate guide on the subject.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Evergreen</strong>: The content remains relevant and valuable over time.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Naturally connects to other pages</strong>: Cornerstone content often links to and from other related articles on your website, creating a web of internal links.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we proceed, letâ€™s quickly look at an example of cornerstone content to give you an idea of what it looks like. Let&#8217;s look at WPBeginnerâ€™s <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/start-a-wordpress-blog/\">How to Start a WordPress Blog in 2023 (Beginnerâ€™s Guide)</a>. Here are some of the topics covered in the blog:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"518\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-wpbeginner-example.png\" alt=\"Example of cornerstone content on WPBeginner.\" class=\"wp-image-242358\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-wpbeginner-example.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-wpbeginner-example-300x221.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-wpbeginner-example-600x443.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A closer look at the site will show that each of the topics covered is an individual blog post. They all form a cluster around the primary article.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-importance-of-cornerstone-content-for-seo\">The Importance of Cornerstone Content for SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The important role of cornerstone content in SEO canâ€™t be overstated. Here are a few reasons why it&#8217;s crucial:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-improved-search-rankings\">Improved Search Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Well-structured cornerstone content can boost your site&#8217;s search engine rankings, especially for competitive keywords. One reason for this is that cornerstone content often covers a topic comprehensively.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason is the strategic internal links built to and from the content. These help search engines better <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-crawling-and-indexing/\" title=\"What is Crawling and Indexing in SEO? [Beginners Guide]\">crawl and index your site</a> and understand the relationships between different pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-enhanced-user-experience\">Enhanced User Experience&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornerstone content provides visitors with comprehensive information, making their experience more valuable. This can lead to longer visits, reduced bounce rates, and increased user engagement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-authority-building\">Authority Building</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornerstone content provides the best opportunity to build topical authority. Itâ€™s an excellent tool for establishing your website as a go-to source for information in your niche. This results in your brand gaining the trust of both users and search engines. It also boosts your brand awareness.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With authority and trust being the currency of the internet, gaining these is crucial to your success as a publisher or business owner.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-internal-linking-the-key-to-optimizing-cornerstone-content-in-wordpress\">Internal Linking: The Key to Optimizing Cornerstone Content in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornerstone content never stands alone. It should have other smaller pieces of content linking to it. Called topic clusters, these are articles that each focus and go in-depth on each subtopic covered in your cornerstone content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These links must not be random but strategically built.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are 2 of the most common ways you can build links to your cornerstone content:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-manual-internal-linking\">Manual Internal Linking</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first way to create cornerstone content is by manually creating links to and from your cornerstone content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google can be your ally here as you can use the site search operator to find relevant URLs right on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs). To use this tool, go to Google and search for &#8220;<em>site:example.com.</em>&#8221; This will show you all the indexed content on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"418\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-site-search.png\" alt=\"Find internal links using Google\'s site search operator.\" class=\"wp-image-242368\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-site-search.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-site-search-300x179.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-site-search-600x358.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also refine your search by adding a relevant keyword to your search criteria. For example, &#8220;<em>site:example.com wordpress SEO.â€</em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-site-search.png\" alt=\"Find internal links using Google\'s site search operator and keyword.\" class=\"wp-image-242360\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-site-search.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-site-search-300x236.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/what-is-cornerstone-content-site-search-600x472.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps narrow down your search to articles relevant to your cornerstone content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once youâ€™ve identified your target articles, you can insert a link to your cornerstone post. To do this, open each article in WordPressâ€™s editor mode, go to the section you want to add the link and highlight the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-anchor-text-and-how-does-it-impact-seo/\" title=\"What is Anchor Text and How Does it Impact Your SEO?\">anchor text</a>. Click on the link icon:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"383\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-wp-link-icon.png\" alt=\"Click the link icon to add a link in WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-242369\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-wp-link-icon.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-wp-link-icon-300x164.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-wp-link-icon-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking the link icon will open a window where you can paste the link you copied.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"498\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-paste-link.png\" alt=\"Pasting link into the insert link field.\" class=\"wp-image-242371\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-paste-link.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-paste-link-300x213.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/how-to-find-internal-links-paste-link-600x426.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Youâ€™ll also be given <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-guide-nofollow-sponsored-ugc-links/\" title=\"An SEO Guide to Nofollow, Sponsored, and UGC Links\">internal link settings options</a> that include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Open in new tab</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add â€œnofollowâ€ to link</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add â€œsponsoredâ€ to link</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add â€œugcâ€ to link</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add title attribute to link</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once youâ€™ve selected your settings, press <strong>Enter</strong> to add the link. And your link will be added.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Repeat this process for all the articles you want to link to your cornerstone content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, manually creating cornerstone content is laborious. Thatâ€™s why we would like to show you an easier way.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-using-the-cornerstone-content-feature-in-aioseo\">Using the Cornerstone Content Feature in AIOSEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The easiest way to build internal links to your cornerstone content is to use a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and is trusted by over 3 million savvy website owners and marketers to help them dominate SERPs. Itâ€™s also a powerful plugin that can help you drive relevant traffic to your site. The plugin has many <a